t things. An warrior are about 13-15, and a warrior is about 16-19. Beware of the preists, they could kill me in 3 hits, I got hit for 75 damgae 3 times,luckily I had 4 HP left , sat, and the rest of my group handled it. If you are under 15, don't pull in Oasis. Watch out for deepwater crocs, I don't know if they aggro or attack passer byers, but they do con red to my 13th war. They are liek 17-19, and crocs are locer, like 14-16 I beleive. And please do not rely on the info I am providng, whiel I know most is tru, I may have a few mistakes, such as saying a instead of an in the wrong place. I only try to provide accurte information, so, please don't blame me. Um, nd print out the map of OOm at <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.eqatlas.com">www.eqatlas.com</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> they have very good maps. And if your looking for a group go to the docks and just shout from there or invite, or whatever.  Ok, I think this and the info on that other topic is all I have of NRO and Oasis.<br>
